buyersBonus.name: Auto Repair Expense Reimbursement
buyersBonus.description: Reimburses 20% of the payment, if any, made to repair the vehicle purchased through the car buying program.  Covers up to a $500 reimbursement on repair (parts included) 2x a year (service not available in New Hampshire or New York).

buyersBonus.name: Auto Deductible Reimbursement
buyersBonus.description: Reimburses what you've paid, if anything, for your insurance deductible when you file a claim.  Covers up to $500 2x a year (service not available in New Hampshire or New York).

buyersBonus.name: Auto Expert Opinion
buyersBonus.description: Talk directly to a certified mechanic to discuss questions you might have on recommended repairs and cost, sounds your car is making, etc.  Unlimited use.
